Itaquitinga
Itaquitinga is a city located in the state of Pernambuco, Brazil. Located  at 84 km away from Recife, capital of the state of Pernambuco. Has an estimated (Ibge 2009) population of 15.507 inhabitants.

Economy
The main economic activities in Itaquitinga are based in agribusiness, especially sugarcane (over 477,000 tons) and livestock such as cattle and chickens.
